      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of wear, and all electronic features and climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history and a smooth, powerful engine that runs like new. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that has been meticulously cared for and garaged its entire life.",
