      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle transcends the typical pre-owned category, offering a showroom-grade aesthetic and flawless mechanical integrity. Every contour and interior surface reflects a history of meticulous stewardship, ensuring an ownership experience indistinguishable from new. We invite the most discerning clientele to evaluate this peerless acquisition.",
