    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this beauty to believe it! I've treated this car like my own child\u2014it's in absolutely stunning, showroom condition. Not a single scratch or smudge anywhere! It drives like a dream and smells brand new. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be obsessed with it. \u2728 Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
